title: A-Prince
text:
A-Prince (Korean: 에이프린스) was a South Korean boy band formed by New Planet Entertainment in Seoul, South Korea. The group debuted on July 25, 2012, with "You're The Only One".


== Members ==
Sungwon (성원)
Minhyuk (민혁)
Seungjun (승준)
Siyoon (시윤)
Woobin (우빈)
